From the house of Titan and belonging to the ultra-stylish and sophisticated Karishma series of women’s analog watches is this absolute stunner of a timepiece. Designed with intricate curves a fashionable metal strap and a very sophisticated metallic finish gives this Titan Karishma Analog Watch is a perfect choice for a variety of occasions.

Body and Design

This specialized ladies’ watch from Titan’s Karishma collection comes with an oval shaped dial. This dial contains a watch face that carries a very light solid colour as the dial’s background. The narrow and slightly elongated dial sits perfectly on your wrist while being held together by a very stylish and classy sheet metal strap that features a highly attractive two tone metallic finish.

The Dial has a protective case composed entirely of brass and neatly follows the dial’s outline giving the watch a much needed amount of shock and damage resistance. The top and bottom ends of the dial have a small but detailed petal which comes as an extension of the dial. The watch hands are also given a metallic finish to go with the dial’s brass case which against the light background makes it extremely easy to read the time. The time adjustment or the position change of the watch hands can easily be carried out by using its rotating screw crown that is found on the right side of the dial.

Functions and Other Features

The use of a mineral glass cover gives it a heightened level of scratch resistance while also working with the sturdy brass case to give this Raga series watch from Titan a water-resistant capability of up to 30 m. Together these finely detailed elements on this watch flawlessly come together to give an overwhelming aesthetic value along with accuracy and durability.
